                    <list>
                        <label>5.</label>
                        <item>The withdrawal should be accomplished in three or four increments,
                            each large enough and sufficiently spaced to obtain news prominence and
                            coverage. The first increment, clearly the most important from a
                            publicity viewpoint, should therefore contain more colorful units, a
                            wide spectrum of skills, and representatives from all Services. The
                            first increment is composed tentatively of the following units:</item>
                    </list>
